# Frontend Environment Configuration
# Copy this to .env and customize for your environment

# ===========================
# API Configuration
# ===========================

# Backend API Base URL
# IMPORTANT: Must include the /api suffix
# 
# For Local Development:
#   VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:8000/api
#
# For Production (Koyeb):
#   VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://raga-rasa-backend-[randomid].koyeb.app/api
#
VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://raga-rasa-backend.onrender.com/api

# ===========================
# IMPORTANT NOTES
# ===========================

# 1. API Base URL MUST include /api suffix
# 2. In development: vite.config.ts proxies /api to http://localhost:8000/api
# 3. In production: Use full backend URL via VITE_API_BASE_URL
# 4. When deploying to Koyeb, update this URL to your Koyeb backend URL
# 5. No CORS issues if backend ALLOWED_ORIGINS includes the frontend URL

